        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Wrapped it together.—Rolled it up. Here only. (Comp. “my substance,” or “mass,” Psalm 139:16; “blue mantles,” Ezekiel 27:24, from the same root.) LXX., εἵλησεν; Vulg., “involvit;” Syriac, “rolled it up.”",
