        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Smote the waters.—A symbolical action like that of Moses smiting the rock, or stretching out his rod over the sea. (Comp. also the use of Elisha’s staff, 2Kings 4:29.) In all these cases the outward and visible sign is made the channel of the invisible and spiritual force of faith.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Smote the waters.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
